r heating systems to perform more efficiently. Water recirculation pumps can be installed to deliver instant hot water to your water heating system.\n\n<strong>Gas Line Installation and Repair:</strong>\n\nWe service residential and commercial gas distribution systems. We install gas lines to serve fire places, swimming pool heaters, and other common appliances. We will also detect and repair gas leaks.\n\n<strong>Water and Sewer Lines:</strong>\n\nIf you are need of a water or sewer line repair or replacement, whether your leak is in the yard or under the slab, we will promptly be at you service.\n\n<strong>Video Inspection of Drains &amp; Sewers:</strong>\n\nA video camera is used to view the inside of a drain or sewer pipe. Video inspection allows for the most accurate diagnoses of sewer and drain problems while allowing the piping system to remain in place.\n\n<strong>Underground Water Line, Sewer, &amp; Drain Location :</strong>\n\nSpecial equipment is used to locate underground water and sewer lines without digging. The lines are marked. This service is often used in combination with other services such as leak detection or polybutylene replacement.\n\n<strong>Sewer &amp; Drain Cleaning:</strong>\n\nHave you noticed your sinks or drains getting clogged or draining slow? We will provide professional sewer and drain cleanings for both residential and commercial clientele.\n\n<strong>Yard or Sprinkler Leaks:</strong>\n\nFinally you can have the confidence that you are no longer wasting water through your leaky sprinkler system. Our professionals can locate and repair your yard leak so that you are no longer washing water down the curb.\n\n<strong>Repair or Replace Faucets:</strong>\n\nWe will complete all plumbing repairs faucets inside and out, including your kitchen sink. Should you need a new faucet installed, we will also gladly be at your service.\n\n<strong>Polybutylene (Quest) Replacement/Repair:</strong>\n\nIf your blue polybutylene water service line needs to be replaced and if you want it replaced. Contact us for repair or replacement.','Services','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision','','','2011-09-23 18:07:37','2011-09-23 18:07:37','',10,'http://prontoplumbingdfw.com/10-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(7,88889,'2011-10-19 15:40:48','2011-10-19 15:40:48','','test1','','inherit','closed','open','','test1','','','2011-10-19 15:40:48','2011-10-19 15:40:48','',0,'http://prontoplumbingdfw.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/test1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(10,88889,'2011-09-23 18:07:37','2011-09-23 18:07:37','<strong><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-29\" title=\"plumbingservices1\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://prontoplumbingdfw.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/plumbingservices1.jpg\" width=\"310\" height=\"150\" /></strong>\r\n\r\nHere at Pronto Plumbing we want to be your local plumbing experts. We handle all types of plumbing repairs such as faucet repairs, sink repairs, toilet repairs, shower repairs, broken or leaking pipes, etc. If you have any questions feel free to <a href=\"http://prontoplumbingdfw.com/contact/\">give us a call</a>.\r\n\r\n<strong>Water Heaters:</strong>\r\n\r\nWe repair and install water heaters for residential customers throughout the area. We also service existing water heaters and modify water heating systems to perform more efficiently.\r\n\r\n<strong>Leak Detection:</strong>\r\n\r\nleaks of any type can be very annoying. Leaking water pipes are often concealed underground or hidden under slab foundations. The leak can be located without exposing the entire length of the water line. This reduces labor cost and minimizes the work area. For a complete explanation of our leak detection services please tour the leak detection page of this site.\r\n\r\n<strong>Slab Leak Repairs:</strong>\r\n\r\nSlab leaks can be very tricky to spot and diagnose. If you feel you have a slab leak don\'t hesitate to call. Once a leak has been discovered it is essential that the leak is repaired as soon as humanly possible.\r\n\r\n<strong>Gas Line Installation and Repair:</strong>\r\n\r\nDo you suspect an issue with a gas line? We install gas lines to serve common appliances such as fire places, swimming pool heaters, and other common appliances. We will also detect and repair gas leaks.\r\n\r\n<strong>Water and Sewer Lines:</strong>\r\n\r\nWater lines and sewer lines are very important to the convenience of any home or office. If you are need of a water or sewer line repair or replacement, whether your leak is in the yard or under the slab, we will promptly be at you service.\r\n\r\n<strong>Sewer &amp; Drain Cleaning:</strong>\r\n\r\nOne of the most common types of plumbing problem is clogging of drains and sewers.  Have you noticed your sinks or drains getting clogged or draining slowly? We will provide professional sewer and drain cleanings for both residential and commercial clientele.\r\n\r\n<strong>Yard or Sprinkler Leaks:</strong>\r\n\r\nOne of the hidden costs of increased water / utility bills is a leaky sprinkler line. Fixing this can help you reduce water usage. Our professionals can locate and repair your yard leak so that you are no longer washing water down the curb.\r\n\r\n<strong>Repair or Replace Faucets:</strong>\r\n\r\nFaucets, faucets, faucets. The typical home has several faucets so repair or replacement is often just a matter of time. We will complete all plumbing repairs faucets inside and out, including your kitchen sink. Should you need a new faucet installed, we will also gladly be at your service.\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>','Services','','publish','open','open','','services','','','2013-05-08 19:46:04','2013-05-08 19:46:04','',0,'http://clearprofiles.com/plumbing101/?page_id=7',0,'page','',0),(66,1,'2013-05-08 19:45:25','2013-05-08 19:45:25','<strong><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-29\" title=\"plumbingservices1\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://prontoplumbingdfw.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/plumbingservices1.jpg\" width=\"310\" height